accounts

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • accounts.Profile

  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    The Profile class holds all the identifications of a person needed to open accounts. Holds the person's first name, last name, and date-of-birth and is able to return these values. Can also check if two profiles are the same.
    Author:
    Jah C. Speed, Abe Vitangcol
